    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/e15f8ac7d63329119cb803b66c0c60af.avif?t=1682957808\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/e280fd14d16af9ba5253e3aa69e571a4.poster.avif?t=1682957808\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/e280fd14d16af9ba5253e3aa69e571a4.webm?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/e280fd14d16af9ba5253e3aa69e571a4.mp4?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Oxygen Caliber 是一款基于物理的益智解谜游戏，你需要穿越无情的太空<br><br>你的任务将会是通过虫洞在银河系里航行! 不幸的是，当地的行星群挡住了你的去路。运用您的智慧和一些创造力去安全地探索未知的太空区域！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/acb972dc9d86d6c955842a6fa91e7bd9.avif?t=1682957808\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用你手中的工具穿越太空</h2>有策略地使用有限的氧气穿越太空，并用抓钩从一个星球跳到另一个星球！喜欢冒险吗？那就搭上一颗流星看看会去到哪里！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/20578c091dcdaef5d9d23d5a00de2d6f.poster.avif?t=1682957808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/20578c091dcdaef5d9d23d5a00de2d6f.webm?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/20578c091dcdaef5d9d23d5a00de2d6f.mp4?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索银河系</h2>享受各种各样的行星、恒星和小行星！有些想把你吸进来，有些想把你推出去，还有一些戴着炫酷的光环！但要小心，有些行星比其他行星更友好！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验与众不同的宇宙</h2>Oxygen Caliber拥有精美的 2D 图形、出色的音效设计，最重要的是，它营造出一种超凡脱俗的氛围！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/ffebc87be46867fd6b979e312ffb3c23.poster.avif?t=1682957808\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/ffebc87be46867fd6b979e312ffb3c23.webm?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/ffebc87be46867fd6b979e312ffb3c23.mp4?t=1682957808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284990/extras/bf8c4ffa100ef05758924a887aea3fdb.avif?t=1682957808\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Oxygen Caliber 作为 USC 交互设计和制作课的项目，由开发者 Robbie Goldberg 和 Andi Ren 于 2022 年春季创作，音乐由 Justin Petrovych 创作。有关更多信息，请访问我们的发布者页面。要了解有关南加州大学游戏项目（世界排名第一）的更多信息，请访问  USC Games website, linked to the right.",
